ameters you’d like to pass with your placement. These can be referenced within the rules"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of your campaign. Keys beginning with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"$"},{"type":"text","text":" are reserved for Superwall and will be dropped. Values can be any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"JSON encodable value, URLs or Dates. Arrays and dictionaries as values are not supported at this time, and will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be dropped."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"paywallOverrides","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallOverrides"},{"type":"text","text":" object whose parameters override the paywall defaults. Use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to override products and whether it ignores the subscription status. Defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"onRequestDismiss","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An optional completion block that gets called when the paywall should dismiss. This defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" and the SDK"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"presentationMode.wrappedValue.dismiss()"},{"type":"text","text":" by default. Otherwise you must perform the dismissal of the paywall."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"onSkippedView","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A completion block that accepts a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/superwall-ios.SuperwallKit\/documentation\/SuperwallKit\/PaywallSkippedReason"},{"type":"text","text":" and returns an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":". This will show"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"